$$TU^2 = TV^2 + UV^2$$

$$24^2 = TV^2 + 16^2$$

$$576 = TV^2 + 256$$

$$TV^2 = 320$$

$$TV = \sqrt{320}$$

$$\boxed{TV = 16\sqrt{5}. \text{ Final Answer: } \boxed{16\sqrt{5}}}$$
